		The <a href="http://genderandsexuality.uic.edu/">Gender and Sexuality Center</a> provides a safe space to explore <strong>gender identity</strong> and its intersection with other social identities such as race, religion, and class. Call or visit GSC to talk to someone about any of the following: <br>
		<p style="text-align:center">
		<span class="label label-default">Gender Identity Concerns   </span> 
		<span class="label label-default">Coming Out   </span> 
