	<div class="panel-heading">
		<h3 class="h3">Considering procedures for surgical gender transition and would like to talk to someone about it?   </h3>
	</div>
	<div class="panel-body">
	<p>
		<a href="http://gapadvocates.webhost.uic.edu/">GAP Advocates @ UIC</a> are students, faculty, and staff trained to be student-centered and trauma informed resources for students considering surgery for gender reassignment.  Their primary purpose is to provide the best quality of care for you by being someone who will listen, support, and connect you with resources. <br>

		<p style="text-align:center"><strong>GAP Advocates @ UIC</strong><br>
	<i class="fa fa-globe"></i> <a href="http://gapadvocates.webhost.uic.edu/"> gapadvocates.webhost.uic.edu</a> <br>
