	<i class="fa fa-phone"></i> (312) 996-8670<br>
	<i class="fa fa-envelope"></i> oae@uic.edu<br>
	<i class="fa fa-globe"></i> <a href="http://oae.uic.edu/">oae.uic.edu</a></p>
	
